-Discuss on conference call:
 -Should we add a line-item reject to the approval process?
  -pros:
    -users would not have to resubmit requests
    -reviewers would not have to reevaluate the new request
  -cons:
    -a partial accept could confuse users
    -We would need very clear language on the accept notification
      to make the partial accept different from the full accept
    -Would need a way for a user to cancel a request after it
      was partially accepted.

- use line item veto per tissue and per monkey

